The paper discusses the limitations of Graph Convolutional Networks (GCN) and compares it with other architectures like GraphCNN and ResNet-18 on 2D images. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE), and Social and Information Networks (cs.SI).
